  <brief_title>Preventive Effects of Ginseng Against Atherosclerosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Preventive Effects of Ginseng Against Atherosclerosis and Subsequent Ischemic Stroke: A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
